Henrique Ben David (born 5 December 1926 - deceased 4 December 1978) was a Portuguese footballer who played for Atltico, as a forward. Ben David made his national debut against England 14 May 1950 in Lisbon and scored 2 goals in a 3-5 loss. He gained 6 caps and scored 4 goals for the Portuguese national team. 
